"context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6819,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/21\/umar-competes-with-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":42794,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Competition: Umar tries to compete with Abu Bakr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, ordered us to give charity and at the time I had some wealth. I said to myself, \u201cToday I will outdo Abu Bakr, if ever there were a day to outdo him.\u201d I went with half\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6100,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/09\/sahabah-prophet-gone-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":42794,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sahaba: If the Prophet is gone, go to Abu Bakr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 9, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Jubayr ibn Mut\u2019im reported: A woman came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he ordered her to return another time. She said, \u201cWhat if I come and I do not find you?\u201d It was as if she wanted to say, \"What if I find you dead?\"\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text